islab.parvecmf.factorizer

Class ParVecMFFactorizer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.mahout.cf.taste.impl.recommender.svd.AbstractFactorizer
      • islab.parvecmf.factorizer.ParVecMFFactorizer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Refreshable, Factorizer

    public class ParVecMFFactorizer
extends AbstractFactorizer
    Implements the ParVecMF methodology, as described in "ParVecMF: A Paragraph Vector-based Matrix Factorization Recommender System" and in "From Free-text User Reviews to Product Recommendation using Paragraph Vectors and Matrix Factorization".

    See a working example here.

                   throws TasteException
        Create the factorizer
        Parameters:
        model - A DataModel containing user-to-item ratings
        idm - An IDMigrator that maps alphanumerical user and item ids to numerical values
        numFeatures - Total number of features
        strUserModel - Location of the file containing the user paragraph vectors (see README.md and the example code for details)
        strItemModel - Location of the file containing the item paragraph vectors (see README.md and the example code for details)
        numIterations - Number of iterations
        lu - λu hyperparameter
        lv - λv hyperparameter
        c - c hyperparameter
        numTrainingThreads - Number of training threads
        Throws:
        TasteException - In case of error
